<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Link inválido</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; margin: 0; min-height: 100vh; background: #f6f5fb; color: #3b2f6e; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .box { text-align: center; max-width: 380px; }
    .icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin: 0 0 .4rem; }
    p { margin: 0; font-size: .9rem; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.5; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="box">
    <div class="icon">🔒</div>
    <h1>Link inválido ou expirado</h1>
    <p>Peça à sua agência um novo link de conexão.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
